<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="recreation-n">recreation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌrekri'eɪʃn/    美 /ˌrekri'eɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] 消遣；娱乐；[C] 娱乐 / 消遣活动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We play basketball once a week for recreation. 
我们每周打一次篮球作为娱乐。</p></div></div>